[[ru/Manual/Base Set/Cargos/Сталь|Сталь]] is a strong and useful metal made chiefly from [[en/Manual/Base Set/Cargos/Iron Ore]] using large furnaces at the [[en/Manual/Base Set/Industries/Steel Mill]].  It is then sent to the factory for use in the [[en/Manual/Base Set/Cargos/Goods]] manufacturing process.

